      "raceComments": "{\"comment\":\"4. ZIPPING VIOLET boasts strong form at this course and distance having won three times from six starts. Recorded a 1.3 lengths win (29.89) in a Grade 5 last time at this track. Looks suited and should go close. 1. VALLEY CASH jumped cleanly and went straight to the lead, holding on for a place when third (30.23) at this track in a Grade 5 over 520m. The form from her last run is stacking up nicely. Will give a great sight again. 7. HARMONY KEEPING was in the placings last time but three back clocked a sharp 18.23 win over 320m at Richmond. Must include on winning run three back. 2. FASCINATE KATH has ability and can feature with the right run after missing a cheque here most recently.\",\"runners\":[4,1,7,2],\"exclusive\":false}",
